Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DigitalDoily
    Main entry point for application, simply creates an initialises a new frame
    DoilyFrame
    JFrame which contains and sets up various components, but does not control the actual drawing (this is handled by DoilyPanel)
    DoilyPanel
    JPanel that provides the main drawing area and an interface to change properties like pen size etc.
    DrawPoint
    Represents an individual point which is displayed on the screen.
    GalleryImage
    Represents a single image that is used to save a state of the drawing into the gallery.
